flowchart LR
  Operator[Operator or PM] --> Browser[Task detail and refinement client]
  Reviewer[Architect UX QA SRE Principal] --> Browser
  Browser --> API[Audit HTTP API]
  API --> Auth[Bearer token and role checks]
  API --> Refinement[Execution Contract refinement helper]
  Refinement --> Domain[Execution Contract domain module]
  Domain --> Store[Append-only audit store]
  Store --> Projection[Task detail and contract projection]
  Projection --> Browser
  Domain --> Report[Verification report skeleton]
  Domain --> Artifacts[User story and refinement artifacts]
  Store --> Metrics[Prometheus metrics endpoint]
  Metrics --> Dashboard[Refinement dashboard and alerts]
